# UI Components Policy

- Any new reusable UI component must be created in `design-system/components/`.
- Export every added component from `design-system/components/index.ts` and `design-system/index.ts`.
- Add a Storybook story in `design-system/stories/` for each new component.
- App code in `src/` should consume UI components from `design-system` instead of re-implementing them locally.
- If only styling is needed, prefer extending an existing design-system component over creating app-local UI widgets.

## Definition of Done for UI changes

- Component exists in `design-system/components/`.
- Public exports are updated.
- Storybook story demonstrates the component states/interactions.
- App uses the design-system component.
